CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, pg. 15 reads: "4. The Bell Telephone booth attracted thousands with their informative demonstrations by Jim Fitzsimmons, Terry D'Angelo, Jane Ross, Flossie Felser and Herman Hawk."
